query-builder-intro-text: La konstruktero di demandi (''Wikidata Query Builder'') furnisas visual interfacio* por krear simpla demando. Ol esas multe utila por uzeri kun poka o nula konoco pri [$1 SPARQL], la povoza demando-linguo. Query Builder ne uzas omna resursi de SPARQL, ma vu sempre povas sendar vua demando uzanta Query Service, e vu povas vidar, redaktar od expansar ol tra la ligilo super la rezulti. [$2 'Feedback' aceptesas hike].
query-builder-input-value-tooltip: The value field contains the concrete information used to describe an item. For example, "blue" is one possible value for the property "color".
query-builder-property-lookup-tooltip: The property field in a condition, is the category or descriptor for the value. For example, "color" would be a property you'd likely use for the value "blue".
query-builder-property-lookup-limited-su: Propraji kun limitizita suporto ne povas selektesar segun valoro
query-builder-result-error-empty-form: Semblas ke la konstruktero di demandi (''Query Builder'') esis vakua. Komence, voluntez furnisar valida demando, pose probez itere.
query-builder-result-error-incomplete-fo: Un o plusa feldi esas vakua, o havas neagnoskata informo. Voluntez solvar omna problemi e probar itere.
query-builder-reference-relation-tooltip: Vu povas obtenar plu preciza rezulti montranta li kun o sen referi.
query-builder-condition-placeholder: Adjuntez kondiciono, por komencar la konstrukto di questiono ('query')
query-builder-limit-number-results-descr: Limitar la quanto di rezulti a
query-builder-label-opt-out: Montrez identifikili (ID) vice etiketi (to povas preventar tempo-exhausto)
query-builder-include-subclasses: Include related values in the search (recommended)
query-builder-include-subclasses-tooltip: Includes values from subsets of the selected value, e.g., when filtering for "school → located in the administrative territorial entity → Greece", also include "school → located in... → Athens" in the results. Checking this box will likely result in a more complete list of results. Uncheck if you need to see only exact matches for the selected value.
query-builder-quantity-value-error-unit: Please select a valid unit or remove input
query-builder-quantity-value-error-numbe: Please enter a number and select a valid unit or remove input
query-builder-date-input-calendar-notice: Omna dati interpretesas segun Gregoriala kalendario
